snippet.title: Survivor Of Stalking
snippet.description: I am a survivor of all types of abuse, stalking, slander, identity theft, cyber bullying and more. I WILL NOT BE SILENCED NO MATTER WHAT THOSE MONSTERS TRY AND DO. They have already falsified police reports, animal welfare reports, DHS reports and even committed perjury for over a year and a half in court. ATTEMPTING to bring me down. I am standing tall BY GOD'S GRACE and the love of my family and friends. I am blessed and nothing will stop me from moving forward and building an amazing life for myself. I like to write, sing, listen to music, play video games and hang out with family and friends. The psychotic stalkers need to stop being jealous and butt hurt because my life is better and I'm better then their "life" God has me and God has my family and friends.
